                </div>
                <div class="part-badge">Part D of 4</div>
                <h1 class="article-title">ROE Thought Experiment</h1>
                <p class="article-subtitle">Bankers are rightfully focused on metrics like Return on Equity (ROE) and risk-adjusted returns. What might the actual numbers look like for a mid-sized bank implementing Bitcoin products?</p>
                <div class="article-meta">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
                        </svg>
                        Galoy Team
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                            <polyline points="12,6 12,12 16,14"/>
                        </svg>
                        8 min read
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
